Title: KitchenAid® 2 Slice, One-touch motorized lift control Toaster with LCD display
Description: KitchenAid® 2 Slice, One-touch motorized lift control Toaster with LCD display with digital progress bar, extra-wide 1.5 inch slots which will accept the thickest bagels, breads or pastries, adjustable shading control which regulates browning of the toast, and a TOAST/CANCEL button.

Title: KitchenAid® 4 Slice, One-touch motorized lift control Toaster with LCD display
Description: KitchenAid® 4 Slice, One-touch motorized lift control Toaster with LCD display with digital progress bar, extra-wide 1.5 inch slots which will accept the thickest bagels, breads or pastries, adjustable shading control which regulates browning of the toast, and a TOAST/CANCEL button.

Title: KitchenAid® Pro Line® Series Waffle Baker
Description: The specially designed double-sided baking unit rotates to allow the batter to coat both upper and lower waffle plates, producing two golden Grand Belgian waffles.

Title: KitchenAid Ultra Power® 4.5 Quart Tilt-Head Stand Mixer
Description: KitchenAid® Ultra Power® model features a 300-watt motor, 4-1/2 quart stainless steel bowl and a tilt-back mixer head design that provides easy access to bowl and beaters.

Title: KitchenAid® 10 inch Countertop Oven
Description: KitchenAid® 10 inch Countertop Oven with full-size oven performance, bake and broil at temperatures up to 450 degrees (F) and 60 minute timer just like your full size oven, and removable broil pan with grill and nonstick interior for easy cleaning

Title: KitchenAid® Refurbished 7-Cup Food Processor
Description: With a 7-cup work bowl, this food processor and its accessories can chop and blend large quantities of ingredients effortlessly. A powerful induction motor produces consistent results, whether processing continuously or using the Pulse control.

Title: KitchenAid® 12 inch Countertop Oven
Description: KitchenAid® 12 inch Countertop Oven with full-size oven performance, bake and broil at temperatures up to 450 degrees (F) and 60 minute timer just like your full size oven, a warm function for reheating leftovers, a toast function for breads, bagels or sandwiches, and removable broil pan with grill and nonstick interior for easy cleaning

Title: KitchenAid® 9-Cup Food Processor with 2 Bowls
Description: An ideal model for the creative cook, this food processor features a medium-capacity, 9-cup work bowl and a powerful induction motor that produces consistent results. Versatile discs handle a variety of tasks, from precise slicing to medium shredding.

Title: KitchenAid® KitchenAId® Refurbished 12-Cup Food Processor with 2 Bowls
Description: The KitchenAId® Refurbished 12-Cup Food Processor with 2 Bowls, 3 Blades and 3 Discs is an ideal model for the creative cook, this food processor features powerful induction motor that produces consistent results. Versatile discs handle a variety of tasks, from precise slicing to medium slicing and shredding.

Title: KitchenAid® Artisan® Series Refurbished 5 Qt. Tilt Head Stand Mixer
Description: KitchenAid® Artisan® Series Refurbished 5 Qt. Tilt Head Stand Mixer model has a 325-watt motor, stainless steel bowl with comfort handle and a tilt-head mixer design that provides easy access to bowl and beaters.
